asset.hookText: http://www.skis.com/Nordica-Wild-Belle-Womens-Skis-2013/277227P,default,pd.html  The Nordica Wild Belle Womens Skis are packed with some cool features so you can travel anywhere you want to on the mountain. Cruise down the groomers or hit the side country, the Hell's Belles ought to be the skis on your feet. The Energy Ca i-Core Construction gives you the best of both worlds: forgiveness in the tip and tail, and better edge grip underfoot. This wood iCore Technology utilizes wood to drop the weight by twenty-percent and an early rise camRock increases your ability to float and maneuver in powder. You'll have the ease of turn initiation. The Nordica Wild Belle Womens Skis are an overall great and versatile pair of skis that you can take to wild side of the mountain.
